# >>> V1.0.0|2023-02-12, Man Hung-Coeng <udc577@126.com>:
#   01. Create.
#
# >>> V1.0.1|2024-01-03, Man Hung-Coeng <udc577@126.com>:
#   01. Update the value of PS1 adapt to more terminal emulators.
#

